eshmun.modelrepair

Class KripkeNextReleaseGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • eshmun.expression.visitor.visitors.AbstractStateSpecsVisitor<java.lang.Boolean,AbstractState>
      • eshmun.modelrepair.KripkeNextReleaseGenerator

  • public class KripkeNextReleaseGenerator
extends AbstractStateSpecsVisitor<java.lang.Boolean,AbstractState>
    This class traverses the structure and specifications in a technique similar to model checking, however the goal of this class is to generate the next-time, and the release formula as discussed in the paper.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Kinan Dak Al Bab
